EC2:- elastic compute cloud
it is a web service provided by aws amazon.com
that allows user to create and manage virtual server called (instatnce) in the cloud
foe ec2 instance helps we can run the mobile apps and web application and backend services


USES OF EC2 :-
-------------
      1) website hosting
      2) running bussiness application
      3) development and testing envirnoment
      4) big data processing
      5) machine learning workload
      6) backup & disaster record

HOW TO LAUNCH INSTANCE:-
-----------------------

     1) login to the aws managment console
     2) search for amazon ec2 and open it
     3) click launch instance
     4) enter an instance name ( eg my server)
     5) choose an amazon machine image (ami)
                 .amazon linux 2023
                 . ubuntu server
                 . windows server
     6) select an instance type:-
                  . free tier: t2 micro or t3 micro
     7) create a key pair
     8) configure storage
     9) revivew all settings
     10) click launch instance
